<#import "taglib/spring.ftl" as spring />
<#include "taglib/taglib.ftl">
<#include "mobile/template/front/general/macro/macro_help.ftl">
<html>
<head>

<title>帮助-android公众号添加到桌面-群侠户外</title>
</head>

<body>

<div class="container" id="body_content">
<@M_homeNavigate/>
<h3 class="text-center">公众号添加到手机桌面</h3>
<p class="text-center">android版</p>

<p class="text-center">执行下列操作之前，请您务必确认<span class="text-success"><strong>开启</strong></span> : 
<br/>安卓手机>设置>应用程序>微信>授权管理>添加到桌面快捷方式</p>
<p>
1.长按二维码，点识别
<img src="/assets/common/help/addToDesktop/1.gif" class="img-responsive" alt="1.长按二维码，点识别"/>
</p>
<p class="bg-warning">
2.点击‘关注公众号’卓玛拉山
<img src="/assets/common/help/addToDesktop/2.gif" class="img-responsive" alt="2.点击‘关注公众号’卓玛拉山"/>
</p>
<p>
3.点击‘右上角’图标
<img src="/assets/common/help/addToDesktop/3.gif" class="img-responsive" alt="3.点击‘右上角’图标"/>
</p>
<p class="bg-warning">
4.继续点击‘右上角 ...’图标
<img src="/assets/common/help/addToDesktop/4.gif" class="img-responsive" alt="4.继续点击‘右上角 ...’图标"/>
</p>
<p class="bg-warning">
5.点击‘设置’
<img src="/assets/common/help/addToDesktop/5.gif" class="img-responsive" alt="5.点击‘设置’"/>
</p>
<p>
6.点击‘添加到桌面’
<img src="/assets/common/help/addToDesktop/6.gif" class="img-responsive" alt="6.点击‘添加到桌面’"/>
</p>
<p class="bg-warning">
7.到手机桌面查看刚添加的快捷图标‘卓玛拉山’
<img src="/assets/common/help/addToDesktop/7.jpg" class="img-responsive" alt="7.到手机桌面查看刚添加的快捷图标‘卓玛拉山’"/>
</p>
<@M_homeNavigate/>
</div>
</body>
</html>